                 div.card-wide.mdl-card.mdl-shadow--2dp
                   div(style="background-size: contain").mdl-card__title.sessiondownload
                   div.mdl-card__supporting-text
                     | Download your current session

               div.mdl-cell.mdl-cell--4-col
                label(for="uploadBtn" data-hook="session-upload")
                 div(data-hook="upload").card-wide.mdl-card.mdl-shadow--2dp
